- 091 (OutputVariable rename guard): intercept at NodePropertiesForm.tsx:217-227 + NodePropertiesDialog.tsx:281-289; reuse canvasValidation TEMPLATE_REF_RE (line 97) + extractTemplateRefs + parseDownstreamNode; add 'outputvar-collision' rule via task-043 per-type loop pattern (canvasValidation.ts:180-184); confirmation dialog via Fluent UI v9 Dialog (NodePropertiesDialog precedent); auto-rename action in canvasStore.
