Anti-patterns called out (10) — most critical: do NOT invent new validation framework, new template regex, new edge type for 'both', new dialog framework, new badge component, new NodeFormProps contract.

Shared coordination note for 091/092/093: there is no built-in connector wiring groupValidationsByNode results into node.data.validationErrors/warnings. Recommend a canvasStore subscription that runs validation on every change. Suggested file-region split for canvasValidation.ts in research doc Section 8.
